  %hr
  %h3{:style => "text-align: center"} Description
  %label{:style => "text-align: center; font-size:14pt; width: 60%; margin: 0 auto;"}
    ProfMash is a website for students to vote for their favorite teachers and courses in a fun and 
    easy way. It's simpler to use than a survey, and it gives students and teachers a clearer representation 
    of the teachers' good qualities, as well as which teachers have been voted as the students' favorites overall.
